      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "Hi, thank you for taking the time to speak with me today. My name is [Name], and I'm a sales representative from Whatfix. I understand that Mercedes Benz is going through a digital transformation, and we believe our Digital Adoption Platform can help enable your clients to navigate this transformation. Can you tell me a little bit about your current digital adoption challenges?"
