      "content": "I understand. Our Digital Adoption Platform can help address these challenges by providing a no-code editor to create in-app guidance, personalized onboarding experiences for your employees and customers, and capabilities to track user behavior and adoption. We can also help you track user adoption and behavior, providing insights to improve energy management and sustainability. Can I show you a demo of our platform?"
