      "user": "Mercedes Benz",
      "content": "Yes, that would be great. I'd love to see how it works."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "Okay, let me just share my screen with you. (shared screen) As you can see, our platform provides a unified and standardized onboarding experience for your diverse workforce, despite legacy systems. We can also help you create customized onboarding experiences for your employees and customers. (demo of In-App Guidance feature)"
